===Bonus DVD===
*''[[Live from Paris]]'' <U+2013> live concert video recorded at the [[Vincennes Racecourse|Hippodrome de Vincennes]] in [[Paris]], France on 4 July 1987
*''Outside It's America'' <U+2013> a 50-minute documentary on the Joshua Tree Tour
*"With or Without You" music video, alternate version
*"Red Hill Mining Town" music video, directed by [[Neil Jordan]]
*[[Easter egg (media)|Easter egg]]: U2's 18 November 1987 performance in Los Angeles as country-spoof band "[[The Dalton Brothers (band)|The Dalton Brothers]]", including "Lucille" and "Lost Highway"

